<H3> <TI>   12 New ASICs, General-Purpose ICs Pass Design Finalization </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    12 New ASICs, General-Purpose ICs Pass Design Finalization </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94P60129A Beijing ZHONGGUO DIANZI BAO [CHINA ELECTRONICS 
NEWS] in Chinese 28 Jan 94 p 1 </F>

<F P=103> 94P60129A </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing ZHONGGUO DIANZI BAO [CHINA ELECTRONICS 
