<TEXT>
ese 28 Ja 
<H3> <TI>   American Chip Maker Scouts Out the Market </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    American Chip Maker Scouts Out the Market </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   40100047A Beijing CHINA DAILY (BUSINESS WEEKLY) in English 
28 Mar 94 p 8 </F>

<F P=103> 40100047A </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing CHINA DAILY (BUSINESS WEEKLY) </F>
