<H3> <TI>   12 Achievements in HTS Technology, Electronic Testing </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    12 Achievements in HTS Technology, Electronic Testing </PHRASE></F></HT>


<TEXT>
Technology   Certified 

<F P=102> 94P60138B Beijing ZHONGGUO DIANZI BAO [CHINA ELECTRONICS 
NEWS] in Chinese 2 Feb 94 p 1 </F>

<F P=103> 94P60138B </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing ZHONGGUO DIANZI BAO [CHINA ELECTRONICS 
