<H3> <TI>   Implementation of Pre-ISDN in Shanghai </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Implementation of Pre-ISDN in Shanghai </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Overview </H4>

<F P=102> 94P60141A Beijing DIANXIN JISHU [TELECOMMUNICATIONS 
TECHNOLOGY] in Chinese No 1, Jan 94 p 45 </F>

<F P=103> 94P60141A </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing DIANXIN JISHU [TELECOMMUNICATIONS 
