[High-Temperature and Specialty Metal Materials] 
  NE-Metalle: Nichteisenmetalle [Non-Ferrous Metals] 
  ODS: Oxiddispersionsgehaertet [Oxide-Dispersion 
Solidification] 
  PA: Polyamides 
  PAI: Polyamidimid [Polyamideimide] 
  PANI: Polyaniline 
  PAR: Polyarylate 
  PBI: Polybenzimidazol [Polybenzimideazole] 
  PC: Polycarbonates 
  PCB: Printed-Circuit-Board-Materials 
  PE: Polyethylene 
  PEEK: Polyaryletherketone 
  PEI: Polyetherimide 
  PEK: Polyetherketone 
  PES: Polyethersulfon [Polyethersulphone] 
  PET: Polyethylenterephtalat [Polyethyleneterephthalate] 
  PF: Phenolharze [Phenol Formaldehyde] 
  PI: Polyimid [Polymer SP] 
  PMMA: Polymethylmethacrylate 
  POM: Polyoxymethylene 
  PP: Polypropylene 
  PPO: Polyphenyloxide 
  PPS: Polyphenylensulfide 
  PPV: Polyphenylenevinylene 
  PS: Polystyrol [Polystyrene] 
  PSU: Polysulfon [Polysulphone] 
  PTFEE: Polytetrafluorethylene 
  PUR: Polyurethane 
  PVC: Polyvinylchloride 
  PVDF: Polyvinylidenfluorid [Polyvinyldifluoride] 
  PVF: Polyvinylfluoride 
  PY: Polypyrrole 
  SIMIT: Sized-Induced-Metal/Insulator-Transition 
  UP: Ungesaettigte Polyester [Unsaturated Polyester] 

