<H3> <TI>   French Minister Outlines S&amp;T Information Program </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    French Minister Outlines S&amp;T Information Program </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94WS0224A Paris AFP SCIENCES in French 27 Jan 94 p 1 </F>
