<H3> <TI>   German Space Agency Announces 1994 Program </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    German Space Agency Announces 1994 Program </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94WS0250B Paris AFP SCIENCES in French 17 Feb 94 p 12 </F>
<F P=103> 94WS0250B </F>
<F P=104>  Paris AFP SCIENCES </F>
<F P=105>  French </F>


