<H3> <TI>   Netherlands: Fokker Reduces Production by 20 Percent </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Netherlands: Fokker Reduces Production by 20 Percent </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94WS0233A Paris LE MONDE in French 16 Feb 94 p 22 </F>
